Package: ravrosr
Title: Confluent Schema Registry Integration and Avro Serialization for R
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Sumal", "Perera", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "dragon.fly.2026@proton.me")
Description: Provides Confluent Schema Registry integration and Avro
    serialization/deserialization for R. The Rust backend (via extendr) handles
    async HTTP communication with Schema Registry, Avro binary encoding/decoding,
    and type conversions between R and Avro. Supports Confluent Cloud
    authentication via API key/secret.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.2)
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc (>= 1.67)
Config/rextendr/version: 0.3.1
Biarch: true
NeedsCompilation: yes
